{"sha": "a585aaefb662ae26f8675955f26fad9be4fea96b", "node_id": "MDY6Q29tbWl0NzI0NzEyOmE1ODVhYWVmYjY2MmFlMjZmODY3NTk1NWYyNmZhZDliZTRmZWE5NmI=", "commit": {"author": {"name": "bors", "email": "bors@rust-lang.org", "date": "2020-10-02T13:22:26Z"}, "committer": {"name": "bors", "email": "bors@rust-lang.org", "date": "2020-10-02T13:22:26Z"}, "message": "Auto merge of #77418 - pietroalbini:ci-environment-files, r=Mark-Simulacrum\n\nSwitch to environment files to change the environment on GHA\n\nThis PR switches our CI to use GitHub's new [environment files](https://docs.github.com/en/free-pro-team@latest/actions/reference/workflow-commands-for-github-actions#environment-files) to set environment variables and add items to `$PATH`, as GitHub [plans to disable the old `::set-env` and `::add-path` log commands](https://github.blog/changelog/2020-10-01-github-actions-deprecating-set-env-and-add-path-commands/) due to a [security issue](https://github.com/actions/toolkit/security/advisories/GHSA-mfwh-5m23-j46w).\n\nOur self-hosted runners are on version 2.273.4, so they already have support for this.\n\nr? `@Mark-Simulacrum`", "tree": {"sha": "1367bbfe331d41eb3421b7aace6b966dc22eb827", "url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rust-lang/rust/git/trees/1367bbfe331d41eb3421b7aace6b966dc22eb827"}, "url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rust-lang/rust/git/commits/a585aaefb662ae26f8675955f26fad9be4fea96b", "comment_count": 0, "verification": {"verified": false, "reason": "unsigned", "signature": null, "payload": null}}, "url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rust-lang/rust/commits/a585aaefb662ae26f8675955f26fad9be4fea96b", "html_url": "https://github.com/rust-lang/rust/commit/a585aaefb662ae26f8675955f26fad9be4fea96b", "comments_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rust-lang/rust/commits/a585aaefb662ae26f8675955f26fad9be4fea96b/comments", "author": {"login": "bors", "id": 3372342, "node_id": "MDQ6VXNlcjMzNzIzNDI=", "avatar_url": "https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/3372342?v=4", "gravatar